comment: /**  * Returns path to xpack codebase path  */
code: /**  * Returns path to xpack codebase path  */ @SuppressForbidden(reason = "looks up path of xpack.jar directly") static Path getElasticsearchCodebase() {     URL url = XPackBuild.class.getProtectionDomain().getCodeSource().getLocation().     try {         return PathUtils.get(url.toURI()).     } catch (URISyntaxException bogus) {         throw new RuntimeException(bogus).     } }
